subject: all tricks and no treat
body:                                                                                                                      https://www.caraveoforcongress.com/[https://www.caraveoforcongress.com/] Peter – the ghosts and monsters outsidearen’t the only scary part of this Halloween. The stakes of this election arenothing less than spooky. To protect our rights this Halloween, can you donatetoday? Donate Now →[https://secure.actblue.com/donate/em_yc_q4_2024?refcode=email_103124_trick-or-treat] My opponent is all tricks and no treat : * He has supported a totalabortion ban with no exceptions for rape or incest, even calling overturningRoe v. Wade a “success”. * He voted against expanding Title X funding, whichprovides essential reproductive healthcare like ultrasounds and affordablecontraception. * He voted against lowering insurance premiums and prescriptioncosts, capping the price of life-saving medication, and cutting hospital fees.* In Congress, he would have the power to enact this dangerous agenda on anational level. In contrast, I’m dedicated to building a future that protectsabortion rights, lowers costs for families, and provides affordable healthcarefor everyone. To create that future and fight back against my opponent’s scaryagenda, I need your help. Can you donate today to help us meet our end-of-month goal this Halloween?
